      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STEREOPHONIC (1) is yet to miss the placings in an excellent record this trip which boasts two wins and two placings. Recorded a 6 length win (25.00) in a Mix last time at this track. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. MOJAVE (2) is a handy dog who jumped from box 5 last time out and scored by 2.5 lengths at this track (25.06). Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. Has hit winning form and can go on with it. SPENCER BANNER (7) carved over from wide out and boxed on strongly to finish 2 lengths away in second (17.78) behind Really Savage at Richmond Straight. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Expected to feature. MARTINI NIGHTS (6) busted the clock to salute last start. Big chance on that form.",
